<div style="background-color: #f8fafc; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 40px 20px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.6;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);">
    <!-- Decorative Header Line -->
    <div style="height: 6px; background: linear-gradient(to right, #4f46e5, #0ea5e9);"></div>
    
    <!-- Email Body Container -->
    <div style="padding: 32px 40px;">
      <!-- Company Branding -->
      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;">
        <span style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Scrum<span style="color: #4f46e5;">.co.id</span></span>
        <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 2px;">Notifikasi Pesan Baru</div>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 15px; margin-top: 0; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600;">Halo Admin,</p>
      
      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Anda telah menerima pesan kontak baru dari situs Scrum.co.id. Berikut adalah rincian pesan tersebut:
      </p>

      <!-- Details Summary Card -->
      <div style="background-color: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px;">
          <tr>
            <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 8px; width: 140px; vertical-align: top;">Nama Pengirim</td>
            <td style="color: #0f172a; padding-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;"><%= @contact_message.name %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 8px; vertical-align: top;">Alamat Email</td>
            <td style="color: #0f172a; padding-bottom: 8px;"><%= @contact_message.email %></td>
          </tr>
          <% if @contact_message.company.present? %>
            <tr>
              <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 8px; vertical-align: top;">Perusahaan</td>
              <td style="color: #0f172a; padding-bottom: 8px;"><%= @contact_message.company %></td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>
          <tr>
            <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; padding-bottom: 8px; vertical-align: top;">Subjek</td>
            <td style="color: #0f172a; padding-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;"><%= @contact_message.subject %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="font-weight: 700; color: #64748b; vertical-align: top; padding-top: 8px; border-top: 1px dashed #e2e8f0;">Pesan</td>
            <td style="color: #0F172A; padding-top: 8px; border-top: 1px dashed #e2e8f0; white-space: pre-wrap; font-style: italic;"><%= @contact_message.message %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <%= link_to "Buka di Dashboard Admin", admin_contact_message_url(@contact_message), style: "display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; background-color: #4f46e5; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2);" %>
      </div>

      <div style="border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; padding-top: 20px; font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center;">
        Email ini dikirim secara otomatis oleh sistem Scrum.co.id.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
